{"tid":896112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最悶的sticker上線啦 Telegram + Whatsapp (Android only)","createTime":"2018-11-09T17:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T04:39:07.000Z","uid":71237,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6865cec229d31ab625bdc0e8cc67ae92ab473c9c","tid":896112,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T17:26:36.000Z","msg":"Outliers Economics sticker系列！絕對係史上最悶的sticker！<br />\nTelegram + Android的whatsapp用家可以使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/012455_d7686cea352c6857b987a9d4fd4820b7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F012455_d7686cea352c6857b987a9d4fd4820b7.PNG&h=21a475a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己都唔預有人會用。<br />\n勉強要搵用途嘅話，如果你係學生，可以睇住嚟溫書。<br />\n如果你係教育工作者，回答學生問題的時候可以使用。<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1. 如何使用？<br />\nA1. 請按以下連結<br />\nAndroid的whatsapp用家：<a href=\"https://outliersecon.page.link/WhatsappStickerAndroid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foutliersecon.page.link%2FWhatsappStickerAndroid&d=16WE%2Fo1bQeGnNGmo9ydHpfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=88c0f46b\" target=\"_blank\">https://outliersecon.page.link/WhatsappStickerAndroid</a><br />\niOs的whatsapp用家：未能使用<br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://outliersecon.page.link/TelegramSticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foutliersecon.page.link%2FTelegramSticker&d=16WE%2Fo1bQeGnNGmo9ydHpfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5f2a34e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://outliersecon.page.link/TelegramSticker</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2. 點解要整咁無聊的sticker？<br />\nA2. 其實我都唔認為有人傾計嗰陣會用。只係學識咗點樣整sticker之後，將一堆本身畫好咗嘅圖整做sticker。<br />\n勉強要搵用途嘅話，如果你係學生，可以睇住嚟溫書。<br />\n如果你係教育工作者，回答學生問題的時候可以使用。<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 你點樣整sticker？<br />\nA3. 用Word畫完之後copy去小畫家<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 點解唔退地？<br />\nA4. 退咗地就睇唔清啲線<br />\n<br />\nQ5. 以後仲會唔會更新？<br />\nA5. whatsapp版的sticker數量有限，所以除非大家有好提議，否則應該唔會再更新。<br />\nTelegram版就會不斷更新。大家有咩圖想我加落去可以出聲，DSE有關的優先。<br />\n遲啲可能會畫埋大學ECON的圖。<br />\n<br />\nQ6. 你不如真係搵啲經濟學家的相，然後再配文字，整一set真正的sticker。<br />\nA6. 太麻煩，不了。<br />\n<br />\nQ7. 我見到你啲圖有錯漏<br />\nA7. 你可以whatsapp / telegram通知我。<br />\n我的whatsapp：<a href=\"https://outliersecon.page.link/whatsapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foutliersecon.page.link%2Fwhatsapp&d=16WE%2Fo1bQeGnNGmo9ydHpfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fe761d5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://outliersecon.page.link/whatsapp</a><br />\n我的telegram：<a href=\"https://outliersecon.page.link/telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foutliersecon.page.link%2Ftelegram&d=16WE%2Fo1bQeGnNGmo9ydHpfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c7319e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://outliersecon.page.link/telegram</a>"},{"pid":"041d22663c50bd3ab3875a2dc2a885e5888a6eea","tid":896112,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"真係學到嘢架<br />\n例如elastic demand的圖，學校可能淨係會教左手面果種（即係叫你畫得平啲）。<br />\n但其實唔需要專登畫得平啲，右手面果種都得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/014323_b4bf500d159c99936333edc442e3357e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F014323_b4bf500d159c99936333edc442e3357e.PNG&h=0c731079&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ba630bf9814a24d6d8846212f850a3bf4102c90","tid":896112,"uid":172823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"其實係易啲分姐，平啲咪貼近啲完全彈性（水平線）marker同自己易啲睇.."},{"pid":"ddcabacd4fc90b27cbd0df46b0ee8d2e78f9da87","tid":896112,"uid":199200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"等巴打轉做ios<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292509a631d585e4232f7a3a873a242f84727111","tid":896112,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0ba630bf9814a24d6d8846212f850a3bf4102c90","tid":896112,"uid":172823,"like":1